                <head>No. 629.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago de Cuba</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-05-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 26, 1888</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of State</hi>,<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Thompson, minister resident Hayti, telegraphs here by French cable:</p>
                <p>“Advise Secretary State, Washington, send war vessel. Revolution imminent, Port
                    au Prince.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Reimer.</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
